[assistant] Fixed the failure in `ValidatorMessageFactoryTest`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - `UIViewRoot` extends `UIComponentBase`, and constructing it before `FacesContext.setCurrentInstance(context)` caused `FacesContext.getCurrentInstance()` to fall through to `FactoryFinder`, which then tried to load unavailable implementation class `com.sun.faces.util.Util`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Change:
[assistant] - Delayed `UIViewRoot` construction until after the test `FacesContext` is registered as current.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated file:
[assistant] - `tests/src/jakarta.platform/jakarta.jakartaee-api/10.0.0/src/test/java/jakarta_platform/jakarta_jakartaee_api/ValidatorMessageFactoryTest.java`
